{"tid":2245282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★教聯會會長：近年學生北上讀書或會被同學看成「怪物」","createTime":"2020-10-16T05:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T04:33:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":119,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8f0baf57af06688a12acc3ef47d4295a8151db","tid":2245282,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】國家教育部近日指會加強招收香港文憑試學生。教聯會會長黃均瑜認為，應放寬文憑試學生到內地升學的門檻，令在主要科目失手的學生亦可到內地升學。<br />\n<br />\n黃均瑜指，近年學生北上讀書或會被同學看成「怪物」，因此國家主席習近平提出要增強青年對祖國向心力。他認為，難以短期改變年輕人心態，應集中解決學生到內地升學所面對的困難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=409271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409271&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=8643dc95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409271&h=4d2c642f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=409271</a>"},{"pid":"074e2f2c862d5204be1680725172019a659f8d0e","tid":2245282,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d0f096a67b4a6f5f7648991651c2b8fce1a951","tid":2245282,"uid":237562,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"將來要去華僑農場"},{"pid":"8378e828b37432ebec5568c131c38d67bc5ca5f4","tid":2245282,"uid":73942,"like":208,"dislike":0,"score":208,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"都戇鳩，唔係近年，係不嬲都將北上讀書嘅傻閪看成怪物"},{"pid":"492c75a277266df9df60f5ce05e63a726edcb0a3","tid":2245282,"uid":50386,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"ci